That's because every time I go into the manhole and travel in time, the past and present reset themselves.

10
00:00:58,890 --> 00:01:03,010
 You know the camera that you lost the day before I left for the military... 

11
00:01:03,010 --> 00:01:05,130
 I heard that pharmacist guy found it for you. 

