00:01:07,930 --> 00:01:13,010
 I'm thinking that you saw that video message I left you on there if you got the camera back. 

14
00:01:13,010 --> 00:01:16,570
 I never saw a video message like that. 

15
00:01:17,310 --> 00:01:19,530
 Jae Hyeon... 

16
00:01:19,530 --> 00:01:23,620
Ironically, because of the things I've done in the past,

17
00:01:23,620 --> 00:01:26,870
you are becoming closer and closer to Jae Hyeon.

18
00:01:26,870 --> 00:01:29,980
 It wasn't a prank. I meant it. 

19
00:01:29,980 --> 00:01:33,490
Rather, the uncomfortable truths don't reset themselves.

20
00:01:33,490 --> 00:01:34,980
 What? 

21
