 I did that because I like you. 

22
00:01:38,610 --> 00:01:42,110
It's true that Jin Sook likes me, after all.

23
00:01:43,420 --> 00:01:48,200
Soo Jin, what should I do now?

24
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:51,590
How can I  get you back?

