What?

27
00:02:14,150 --> 00:02:15,720
What the heck is this?

28
00:02:17,390 --> 00:02:19,740
Where is this place?

29
00:02:23,330 --> 00:02:24,890
Oh...

30
00:02:24,890 --> 00:02:29,000
What's going on here? Am I trapped?

31
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:31,950
Hey! Hey, manhole!

32
00:02:31,950 --> 00:02:34,620
Hey, you should open up the lid of this!

33
00:02:34,620 --> 00:02:36,470
Hey!

34
