00:27:09,240 --> 00:27:14,530
   

358
00:27:14,530 --> 00:27:16,510
Oh.

359
00:27:16,510 --> 00:27:18,820
Awesome. Awesome.

360
00:27:18,820 --> 00:27:23,770
Jin Sook, Jin Sook, I passed. I passed.

361
00:27:23,770 --> 00:27:26,360
Please give it to me quickly. Quickly.

362
00:27:26,360 --> 00:27:31,470
Oh my. Jin Sook. Finally.

363
00:27:31,470 --> 00:27:35,680
We can't even earn enough for the electricity bill, let alone rent.

364
00:27:35,680 --> 00:27:38,150
What should I do?

365
00:27:38,150 --> 00:27:41,400
Yoon Mi, should we change professions? Should we open a noraebang  (karaoke place) ?

366
00:27:41,400 --> 00:27:46,660
Unni, even if we open a noraebang, it seems it won't last long.

367
00:27:58,230 --> 00:27:59,970
Please, here.

368
00:28:05,970 --> 00:28:09,490
He's here again. The one who doesn't help with our sales.

369
00:28:09,490 --> 00:28:13,240
What are you doing? Give him 500 ml.

370
00:28:13,240 --> 00:28:15,030
Give me a 500 ml.

371
00:28:36,670 --> 00:28:38,830
Excuse me.

372
00:28:38,830 --> 00:28:42,280
What is the address of Miss Mi Ja?

373
00:28:42,280 --> 00:28:44,810
- Why do you ask? 
 - Why?

374
00:28:49,580 --> 00:28:51,560
Just because I'm curious.

375
00:28:51,560 --> 00:28:54,490
I can't sleep when I'm curious.

376
00:28:54,490 --> 00:28:56,870
If you're interested, ask her yourself.

377
00:28:56,870 --> 00:28:58,990
Should I call her?

378
00:28:58,990 --> 00:29:01,230
It's alright.

379
00:29:01,230 --> 00:29:03,000
It's not a bad idea to slowly get to know her...

380
00:29:03,000 --> 00:29:07,340
Unni, Ahjussi is asking where you live.

381
00:29:07,340 --> 00:29:10,200
Tell him earth.

382
00:29:10,200 --> 00:29:12,120
You heard, right?

383
00:29:13,060 --> 00:29:15,370
Is that so?

384
00:29:15,370 --> 00:29:21,300
Ultimately... we live at the same address.

385
00:29:23,210 --> 00:29:28,540
   

386
00:29:29,570 --> 00:29:33,640
- The Bong Pil kebobs are here. Enjoy. 
 - Thank you.

387
00:29:41,720 --> 00:29:44,300
Wow.

388
00:29:44,300 --> 00:29:46,800
Business is really doing well.

389
00:29:59,940 --> 00:30:02,120
Excuse me, another Bong Pil kebob please.

390
00:30:02,120 --> 00:30:04,380
Yes, just a moment.

391
00:30:04,380 --> 00:30:08,820
Ah, really. Pil still bothers me even as a kebob.

392
00:30:14,860 --> 00:30:17,970
Jin Sook, can we talk for a minute?

393
00:30:26,230 --> 00:30:29,580
What is it?

394
00:30:29,580 --> 00:30:35,030
Why did you leave and lock the door when I told you I would make you seaweed soup?

395
00:30:35,030 --> 00:30:38,280
Why are you fussing about seaweed soup when you don't even have seaweed?

396
00:30:38,280 --> 00:30:42,520
And didn't we all say to go to Bongbong Pub today?

397
00:30:43,580 --> 00:30:47,910
You. You, you, you.

398
00:30:47,910 --> 00:30:50,410
It's because you feel bad that you didn't prepare a birthday present for me, right?

399
00:30:50,410 --> 00:30:53,640
No, that's not it. Actually...

400
00:30:53,640 --> 00:30:57,100
I left something at your house earlier.

401
00:30:57,100 --> 00:31:02,500
Really? Then, you should have said so from the start.

402
00:31:02,500 --> 00:31:07,510
I'm really sorry about this. I'll quickly go get it.

403
00:31:07,510 --> 00:31:10,410
- Okay. 
 - Work hard.

404
00:31:13,340 --> 00:31:18,600
What's going on? Why is he frequenting my house?

405
00:31:18,600 --> 00:31:24,920
Per chance it's to give me a surprise party for my birthday?

406
00:31:26,270 --> 00:31:27,860
That rascal.

407
00:31:31,450 --> 00:31:34,820
Oh, where could the letters be?

408
00:31:40,460 --> 00:31:46,070
Seriously... where are they?

409
00:31:51,760 --> 00:31:55,170
   
   

410
00:33:44,790 --> 00:33:48,580
♫ Happy birthday to you.

411
00:33:48,580 --> 00:33:52,040
♫ Happy birthday to you.

412
00:33:52,040 --> 00:33:54,340
Here, a celebratory drink on the house.

413
00:33:54,340 --> 00:33:56,350
- Wow, thank you. 
- Thank you!

414
00:33:56,350 --> 00:34:00,380
♫ Happy birthday, dear Jin Sook.

415
00:34:00,380 --> 00:34:03,710
Oppa, but how come Pil isn't coming?

416
00:34:03,710 --> 00:34:07,180
Pil is not good at studying, but he is smart.

417
00:34:07,180 --> 00:34:12,390
He always finds the most convenient time and place for his body.

418
00:34:12,390 --> 00:34:14,180
Look.

419
00:34:14,180 --> 00:34:18,440
Hey, Bong Pil. How can you show yourself just when we're almost done setting up?

420
00:34:18,440 --> 00:34:22,190
Hyung, Soo Jin isn't here yet?

421
00:34:22,190 --> 00:34:24,590
There she comes.

422
00:34:25,520 --> 00:34:28,530
- This way. 
- Soo Jin, you're here.

423
00:34:28,530 --> 00:34:32,270
Oh, you came with the pharmacist.

424
00:34:32,270 --> 00:34:33,390
Wow.

425
00:34:33,390 --> 00:34:37,450
Wow. This is amazing.

426
00:34:37,450 --> 00:34:40,660
This is Jeong Ae and that's Oppa Dal Soo.

427
00:34:40,660 --> 00:34:44,290
Hey, even if you want to, don't ruin the birthday party.

428
00:34:44,290 --> 00:34:46,720
It took us half of the day to prepare this.

429
00:34:46,720 --> 00:34:49,930
Hyung, today's the day Jin Sook was born, right?

430
00:34:49,930 --> 00:34:53,190
It... probably is. Since it's her birthday.

431
00:34:53,190 --> 00:34:57,120
But on this day, at least one of us will die.

432
00:34:57,120 --> 00:35:00,740
W-What?

433
00:35:00,740 --> 00:35:02,490
Just a moment. One moment.

434
00:35:02,490 --> 00:35:04,190
Okay.

435
00:35:06,610 --> 00:35:12,580
I am getting a phone call at this moment, too. I'll be back after the call.

436
00:35:14,290 --> 00:35:18,580
Yes. No, I have a previous appointment.

437
00:35:18,580 --> 00:35:20,660
Yes.

438
00:35:21,980 --> 00:35:24,550
Yes, I will call you back tomorrow.

439
00:35:24,550 --> 00:35:26,340
Okay.

440
00:35:28,180 --> 00:35:29,890
Hey.

441
00:35:31,200 --> 00:35:34,940
What ill-fated relationship do we have that you're bothering me like this?

442
00:35:34,940 --> 00:35:37,210
What do you mean?

443
00:35:37,210 --> 00:35:43,240
From carefully observing you as I travelled through time and space,

444
00:35:43,240 --> 00:35:48,500
you are smiling kindly, but I already know that you're closer to a devil.

445
00:35:48,500 --> 00:35:49,270
Pardon?

446
00:35:49,270 --> 00:35:51,390
I'm telling you to distance yourself from Soo Jin.

447
00:35:51,390 --> 00:35:54,440
If you don't want to embarrass yourself at a party.

448
00:35:54,440 --> 00:35:56,910
Do you understand?

449
00:36:22,880 --> 00:36:25,730
Gosh, gosh.

450
00:36:25,730 --> 00:36:29,430
If I'm making everyone uncomfortable, I will leave.

451
00:36:29,430 --> 00:36:34,840
N-no. No. Please introduce us to good medicine.

452
00:36:34,840 --> 00:36:38,030
No. You guys should enjoy this time among friends.

453
00:36:38,030 --> 00:36:40,400
Yes, you decided well.

454
00:36:40,400 --> 00:36:43,430
Go home well. I'm extremely uncomfortable.

455
00:36:43,430 --> 00:36:46,160
Hey. You leave. I'm more uncomfortable because of you.

456
00:36:46,160 --> 00:36:48,600
You bastard.

457
00:36:48,600 --> 00:36:51,230
Why are you being embarrassing? Seriously!

458
00:36:51,230 --> 00:36:52,960
Don't worry about him and just stay.

459
00:36:52,960 --> 00:36:57,180
He's not much of a welcomed character either.

460
00:37:04,560 --> 00:37:08,270
No, I will leave now.

461
00:37:09,410 --> 00:37:13,530
- No, it's... I mean... 
- You didn't even get to eat anything.

462
00:37:15,300 --> 00:37:17,210
Y-you punk!

463
00:37:17,210 --> 00:37:21,500
What did I do? I didn't say anything.

464
00:37:26,880 --> 00:37:29,230
Sorry, you must have been very uncomfortable.

465
00:37:29,230 --> 00:37:34,240
No, your friends are personable, enjoyable, and fun.

466
00:37:34,240 --> 00:37:40,730
Perhaps, did Pil say something offensive to you separately?

467
00:37:40,730 --> 00:37:43,440
No, that friend didn't say anything.

468
00:37:43,440 --> 00:37:46,310
Oh, it seems like he did. That punk.

469
00:37:46,310 --> 00:37:48,620
It's really not like that.

470
00:37:48,620 --> 00:37:50,970
I am just busy, so I'm leaving because I have to go.

471
00:37:50,970 --> 00:37:54,830
But you asked if you could come to the birthday party with me,

472
00:37:54,830 --> 00:37:58,230
so it doesn't make sense that you have to leave suddenly because you're busy.

473
00:37:58,230 --> 00:38:01,930
It's not like that. Don't misunderstand.

474
00:38:03,710 --> 00:38:08,330
Honestly, I wanted to get to know your friends.

475
00:38:08,330 --> 00:38:11,670
But if you're too greedy, you get indigestion.

476
00:38:11,670 --> 00:38:15,510
Today, I am satisfied with just saying hello like this.

477
00:38:15,510 --> 00:38:20,310
Go on in quickly. They shouldn't stay uncomfortable because of me.

478
00:38:20,310 --> 00:38:23,550
Either way, thank you for today.

479
00:38:23,550 --> 00:38:25,250
I'm the thankful one.

480
00:38:25,250 --> 00:38:27,860
Then, I'll go.

481
00:38:28,790 --> 00:38:31,250
Go safely.

482
00:38:44,870 --> 00:38:46,900
Surprise!

483
00:38:46,900 --> 00:38:48,500
Here.

484
00:38:48,500 --> 00:38:51,090
- One, two—  
- Wait, wait, wait.

485
00:38:51,090 --> 00:38:53,910
Hey, is Seok Tae making the cake? Why isn't he coming?

486
00:38:53,910 --> 00:38:57,640
Let's push the cake cutting to the after-eating celebration and do the before-eating celebration first.

487
00:38:57,640 --> 00:38:59,320
One, two, three!

