00:38:59,320 --> 00:39:02,380
♫ Happy birthday to you.

489
00:39:02,380 --> 00:39:05,390
♫ Happy birthday to you.

490
00:39:05,390 --> 00:39:08,870
♫ Happy birthday, dear Jin Sook.

491
00:39:08,870 --> 00:39:12,920
♫ Happy birthday to you.

492
00:39:14,730 --> 00:39:18,770
- Happy birthday! 
- Happy birthday!

493
00:39:29,390 --> 00:39:35,050
Jin Sook, happy birthday. No, that's not it.

494
00:39:35,050 --> 00:39:37,230
Jin Sook, happy birthday!

495
00:39:37,230 --> 00:39:38,810
Open it at home.

496
00:39:38,810 --> 00:39:41,610
Thank you. When did you prepare all this?

497
00:39:41,610 --> 00:39:43,980
Wait. My present.

498
00:39:43,980 --> 00:39:45,650
I definitely bought one and brought it.

499
00:39:45,650 --> 00:39:47,260
 He's putting on a show again. 

500
00:39:47,260 --> 00:39:49,230
Hey, if you didn't prepare anything, just sit down.

501
00:39:49,230 --> 00:39:50,350
You're getting all the dust into the air.

502
00:39:50,350 --> 00:39:53,180
Jin Sook knows that you're poor, studying for the civil service exam.

503
00:39:53,180 --> 00:39:56,320
So don't put on a show and why don't you try making a deal using something called conversation?

504
00:39:56,320 --> 00:39:59,900
No, I'm saying that's not it. I really, really bought a present today.

505
00:39:59,900 --> 00:40:03,500
Hey, sit down. I'll pretend that I received one.

506
00:40:03,500 --> 00:40:06,240
Hey, it's not this?

507
00:40:08,880 --> 00:40:11,060
Military mail?

508
00:40:11,060 --> 00:40:12,060
What is it?

